==English==
===Noun===
'''asphalt'''
{{wikipedia}}

#A sticky, black and highly viscous liquid or semi-solid that is present in most crude [[petroleum]]s and in some natural deposits. Asphalt is composed almost entirely of [[bitumen]].
#Often used as an abbreviation for [[asphalt concrete]]. A hard ground covering used for roads and walkways
